description:
Immature - A collection of love ballads for the 80s man

Album composed by Trey Parker and Dave Goodman while they were in High School. I think Parker was 16 when this was recorded. On the Jimmy Fallon show he said they made $500 selling these at their high school and he quit his job at Pizza Hut. Good story.

This is not the whole album, only part of it. It is quite obscure and not all of the tracks have been digitized as it was recorded on cassette. If you have a copy, digitize it.

Full Track List:

Side One:

01 - Dead Ballerina
02 - Au Jus - Missing
03 - I Spit On Your Love
04 - Gotta Find That Train
05 - You Jerk
06 - Gonna Find U and Kill U - Missing

Side Two:

07 - Immature - Missing
08 - Without Lips
09 - You're Not Worth The Dirt On The Lint Between My Toes - Missing
10 - I'm In Love With Myself
11 - Sri Lankan Woman
12 - Twin Brothers In Love
13 - Bitch - Missing

Dead Ballerina is my favorite.
